<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Line profiler</b></p><p>If you want to get line-by-line execution times for your running process, select <span class="shortcut">Profile the Process | Attach Profiler</span> in the <span class="control">Run</span> tool window. When you click <span class="control">Stop Profiling and Show Results</span> or the process finishes, the respective runtime will appear for lines that were executed for a significant amount of time.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij-hints-line-profiler.png" alt="Profiler hints in the editor highlighting hot methods" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>